Join my Discord server: https://discord.gg/w6nzgdr
Exyl's Flute Gang: https://discord.gg/flute

So... why? People would message both Exyl and I saying "hey your logos look alike" and after Exyl got told his logo looked like mine a few too many times, he eventually joined my Discord server back in 2018. That's how we met, we were both cool with the coincidences, and laughed about collabing one day. Then when Ping! started going viral I just commented "nice logo" on his video because I didn't know what else to write and it was this inside joke between us. Then he pinned it and the video got millions of views, and people picked up on our logo's similarity both on YouTube and in our Discord communities. So, spawned from an inside joke, Exyl and I made this song together over the course of about 4 days, as he planned to upload it for April 1st as a joke and we started working on it way too late. Sadly I didn't have any time to contribute to the visuals, and Exyl did those all on his own (and you can notice they're a bit rushed). Oh, also, contrary to common belief, I didn't only work on "my part" of the song, while Exyl is the musical genius here I worked on the entire song 😉

